  "observations": [
    "Universal Activity timeline — same composer (Note/Email/Call/Task/Meeting) reused across Contact, Company, Deal, Ticket detail views",
    "Contact 360-view as three-column shell: identity sidebar (left) + activity timeline (center) + associations sidebar (right)",
    "Polymorphic Activity entity with discriminator (email/call/meeting/note/task) rather than separate tables — single API surface",
    "Deal pipeline as kanban board with drag-drop fired automation hooks (stage change → workflow trigger)",
    "Multiple pipelines per object (Deal: New Business / Renewals / Upsell; Ticket: Support / Bug) — Pipeline as first-class configurable entity",
    "Lifecycle stage as universal funnel state on Contact AND Company, advanced by workflow with manual override",
    "Lists with dynamic vs static dual mode — criteria-based recompute vs manual membership",
    "Workflow editor as visual graph: trigger → branches (if/then, value-compare, random) → actions (email, set property, enrol sequence, webhook, AI)",
    "Sequences (cadences) auto-pause on contact reply — stateful enrollment per contact, not stateless template",
    "Property system as meta-layer: standard + custom properties, grouped, with calculation and score subtypes (formulas + rules)",
    "Inbox as unified channel-agnostic view — email + chat + Messenger + WhatsApp + form submissions as one Conversation entity",
    "Associations as explicit many-to-many entity (Contact↔Company↔Deal↔Ticket) rather than embedded foreign keys",
    "Composer slash-commands for inserting Templates / Snippets inline during email/note authoring",
    "Properties section on detail view organized by PropertyGroup (Contact / Email / Conversion / Recent activity / Buying role / Custom)",
    "Forecast as deal-aggregation with manager rollup — categories Best Case / Commit / Most Likely / Closed",
    "Free CRM baseline + paid Hubs as capability layers — same entities, expanded intents per Hub",
    "Mobile Today screen as cross-aggregate dashboard: tasks + meetings + recent activity unified",
    "Breeze AI actions (summarize note, generate email, predict score) embedded as workflow actions and inline composer assists",
    "Customer Portal — auth-gated subset of Tickets + Knowledge Base for external Customer role (read-mostly with submit)",
    "SLA configuration attached to Pipeline (not Ticket) — pipeline-level policy applied per ticket"
  ]
}